we would like to meet Lord Jiyue.

283
00:12:47,870 --> 00:12:49,150
Please kindly inform him.

284
00:12:50,200 --> 00:12:51,040
Queue up.

285
00:12:51,050 --> 00:12:51,800
Register.

286
00:12:51,800 --> 00:12:53,120
How many hours do we have to wait?

287
00:12:53,440 --> 00:12:54,390
How many hours?

288
00:12:55,080 --> 00:12:55,920
At least

289
00:12:56,030 --> 00:12:56,870
two months.

290
00:12:57,600 --> 00:12:58,440
Two…

291
00:12:59,270 --> 00:13:00,600
That's quite a long time.

292
00:13:01,510 --> 00:13:02,350
Butler,

293
00:13:02,360 --> 00:13:04,660
we two come from afar.

294
00:13:04,870 --> 00:13:06,510
Could you please make an exception?

295
00:13:07,440 --> 00:13:08,280
Look at these people.

296
00:13:08,700 --> 00:13:10,140
Who among them hasn't come from afar?

297
00:13:10,750 --> 00:13:12,030
Some book fans and theater fans,

298
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:13,870
just to catch a glimpse of my Lord,

299
00:13:14,360 --> 00:13:16,030
have settled in this town.

300
00:13:16,630 --> 00:13:17,670
Such a big ego!

301
00:13:18,790 --> 00:13:20,000
Ziqi, Ziqi, wait a moment.

302
00:13:20,270 --> 00:13:22,670
Perhaps we have some other way.

303
00:13:23,150 --> 00:13:23,990
Young Master,

304
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:25,040
are you Ziqi?

305
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:26,080
Yes.

306
00:13:26,550 --> 00:13:28,080
Is it Z-I Zi,

307
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:29,790
- Q-I Qi?
- Yes. What's wrong?

308
00:13:30,840 --> 00:13:31,790
Go and tell the Master,

309
00:13:32,000 --> 00:13:33,370
the person he is waiting for
has arrived.

310
00:13:40,120 --> 00:13:40,960
Please come in.

311
00:13:45,960 --> 00:13:46,800
Please wait a moment.

312
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:48,360
I will go and call my Master.

313
00:13:49,120 --> 00:13:49,960
Thank you.

314
00:13:55,750 --> 00:13:56,960
I'm so nervous.

315
00:13:57,000 --> 00:13:59,320
We are about to meet the famous author.

316
00:13:59,550 --> 00:14:00,390
So what?

317
00:14:01,030 --> 00:14:02,540
We are here to inquire about something,

318
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:04,080
not to pay homage.

319
00:14:06,550 --> 00:14:07,390
Actually,

320
00:14:07,510 --> 00:14:09,750
I have a favorite author too.

321
00:14:10,030 --> 00:14:11,200
He is also a prolific author.

322
00:14:11,960 --> 00:14:13,240
The works he wrote

323
00:14:13,790 --> 00:14:14,630
are warm,

324
00:14:14,870 --> 00:14:15,710
touching

325
00:14:15,870 --> 00:14:16,720
and full of twists.

326
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:19,960
Among them, my favorite book is

327
00:14:24,670 --> 00:14:25,870
- is…
- Is…?

328
00:14:26,870 --> 00:14:28,320
It seems it wasn't written very well.

329
00:14:30,440 --> 00:14:31,280
No, it's not.

330
00:14:31,320 --> 00:14:33,270
I remember his pen name is Fu Zhou.

331
00:14:33,440 --> 00:14:34,280
Did you hear of it?

332
00:14:37,550 --> 00:14:38,390
No.

333
00:14:39,360 --> 00:14:41,200
I'm his number one reader.

334
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:44,870
It would be great if I could
meet him once in this lifetime.

335
00:14:49,400 --> 00:14:50,420
Sorry to keep you waiting.

336
00:14:51,080 --> 00:14:53,480
This is my Master, Lord Jiyue.

337
00:14:53,480 --> 00:14:56,700
(Lord Jiyue)

338
00:14:58,320 --> 00:15:00,320
If he is also an ugly person…

339
00:15:02,870 --> 00:15:04,150
Hello, Lord Jiyue.

340
00:15:04,480 --> 00:15:05,440
We have come abruptly

341
00:15:05,630 --> 00:15:08,910
to ask you an important matter.

342
00:15:09,270 --> 00:15:10,360
Sorry to disturb you.

343
00:15:17,440 --> 00:15:18,320
Young Master,

344
00:15:18,960 --> 00:15:19,910
you are Ziqi, right?

345
00:15:21,790 --> 00:15:22,630
Yes.

346
00:15:24,150 --> 00:15:25,200
Where is your home?

347
00:15:26,390 --> 00:15:28,000
Are your parents

348
00:15:28,270 --> 00:15:29,360
still in good health?

349
00:15:29,510 --> 00:15:31,210
I have no home, no parents.

350
00:15:34,270 --> 00:15:35,120
Age is right.

351
00:15:40,360 --> 00:15:41,200
Young Master,

352
00:15:42,200 --> 00:15:43,390
have you ever felt

353
00:15:43,960 --> 00:15:45,320
when you were young,

354
00:15:46,150 --> 00:15:47,510
there were some things…

355
00:15:48,240 --> 00:15:49,240
well,

356
00:15:49,600 --> 00:15:50,440
right?

357
00:15:51,390 --> 00:15:52,720
What I mean to say is

358
00:15:53,150 --> 00:15:53,990
that

359
00:15:53,990 --> 00:15:57,030
did you feel a bit different

360
00:15:58,080 --> 00:16:00,120
from ordinary people?

361
00:16:00,200 --> 00:16:02,150
Are you asking if I am a half-demon?

362
00:16:06,200 --> 00:16:08,740
You compiled the story
of the Qingyi Marquis and the female demon

363
00:16:08,740 --> 00:16:10,360
into a script and spread it widely,

364
00:16:11,440 --> 00:16:12,790
wasn't it to lure me here?

365
00:16:17,960 --> 00:16:18,800
That's right.

366
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:21,360
I am a half-demon.

367
00:16:22,200 --> 00:16:23,040
So what?

368
00:16:26,320 --> 00:16:27,240
Oh dear!

369
00:16:27,440 --> 00:16:29,030
I finally found you.

370
00:16:30,390 --> 00:16:31,630
- Let go of me.
- I won't.

371
00:16:31,910 --> 00:16:32,750
Let go.

372
00:16:33,070 --> 00:16:33,950
Lin Miaomiao.

373
00:16:33,960 --> 00:16:35,670
Lin Miaomiao, help me pull him away.

374
00:16:37,320 --> 00:16:38,160
Help me.

375
00:16:38,600 --> 00:16:39,480
Lin Miaomiao!

376
00:16:40,080 --> 00:16:41,120
You just stand by? You…

377
00:16:41,910 --> 00:16:42,750
Let go.

378
00:16:47,320 --> 00:16:48,240
Come, come quickly.

379
00:16:48,720 --> 00:16:49,560
Hurry.

380
00:16:52,840 --> 00:16:54,030
I was just too excited.

381
00:16:54,150 --> 00:16:55,030
Please don't mind.

382
00:16:55,360 --> 00:16:56,900
I haven't done anything else these years

383
00:16:56,900 --> 00:16:58,030
except for looking for Ziqi.

384
00:16:58,120 --> 00:17:00,080
Those people either had the wrong age

385
00:17:00,080 --> 00:17:01,390
or their experiences didn't match.

386
00:17:01,500 --> 00:17:02,510
Today I finally found you.

387
00:17:02,510 --> 00:17:03,870
This is almost certain.

388
00:17:04,680 --> 00:17:05,880
My life has been saved.

389
00:17:06,640 --> 00:17:07,750
Who exactly are you?

390
00:17:08,310 --> 00:17:10,160
I am a failed scholar
from a nearby village,

391
00:17:10,240 --> 00:17:11,250
born in an impoverished family.

392
00:17:11,250 --> 00:17:12,990
I can't do either manual labor
or farm work.

393
00:17:12,990 --> 00:17:14,960
I had no choice but to
write scripts for a living.

394
00:17:15,030 --> 00:17:17,880
In the past seven years,
all my bestselling scripts,

395
00:17:18,070 --> 00:17:19,070
without exception,

396
00:17:19,200 --> 00:17:21,070
were not originally written by me.

397
00:17:22,680 --> 00:17:24,070
Isn't that plagiarism?

398
00:17:26,030 --> 00:17:28,310
Girl, your words are really harsh.

399
00:17:29,590 --> 00:17:31,000
What is that?

400
00:17:31,070 --> 00:17:31,910
Come.

401
00:17:33,920 --> 00:17:34,760
Come here.

402
00:17:40,470 --> 00:17:41,320
Girl, let me tell you.

403
00:17:41,920 --> 00:17:43,110
What I did is not plagiarism.

404
00:17:44,030 --> 00:17:45,030
It is borrowing.

405
00:17:45,440 --> 00:17:46,640
Borrowing.

406
00:17:46,950 --> 00:17:48,470
Forget it, I won't talk to you anymore.

407
00:17:49,240 --> 00:17:50,510
Forget it, I'll chat with you.

408
00:17:51,790 --> 00:17:52,750
Ten years ago,

409
00:17:53,310 --> 00:17:54,750
in this Wufang Town,

410
00:17:55,350 --> 00:17:57,350
there was a famous music house

411
00:17:57,640 --> 00:17:59,350
called

412
00:17:59,880 --> 00:18:00,720
Huazhe.

413
00:18:03,000 --> 00:18:03,880
The Huazhe was filled

414
00:18:04,200 --> 00:18:06,920
with beauties

415
00:18:07,400 --> 00:18:10,440
and endless music back then.

416
00:18:10,440 --> 00:18:11,680
(Huazhe)

417
00:18:11,680 --> 00:18:15,070
The owner was called Liuniang.

418
00:18:15,830 --> 00:18:18,790
(Liuniang)
She was an absolutely charming

419
00:18:19,270 --> 00:18:22,030
and remarkable lady
with grace and intelligence.

420
00:18:23,400 --> 00:18:25,920
But one day, for some unknown reason,

421
00:18:26,240 --> 00:18:27,480
Liuniang dismissed

422
00:18:27,480 --> 00:18:29,510
all the female musicians,

423
00:18:30,160 --> 00:18:31,350
and that very night

424
00:18:31,750 --> 00:18:33,110
she set a great fire

425
00:18:33,480 --> 00:18:35,750
to the music house

426
00:18:36,160 --> 00:18:37,830
she had painstakingly managed.

427
00:18:40,110 --> 00:18:43,060
At that time I was a poor scholar.

428
00:18:43,550 --> 00:18:45,380
I originally thought of going there

429
00:18:45,640 --> 00:18:47,400
(Huazhe)
to find some valuable remnants.

430
00:18:47,920 --> 00:18:48,760
Unexpectedly,

431
00:18:49,200 --> 00:18:50,790
I really found something.

432
00:19:11,350 --> 00:19:13,640
I was overjoyed when I saw the pearls.

433
00:19:14,270 --> 00:19:16,160
I thought it was a windfall.

434
00:19:16,830 --> 00:19:19,310
But after I took them,

435
00:19:19,680 --> 00:19:20,720
I realized these pearls

436
00:19:21,960 --> 00:19:23,480
were so mysterious.

437
00:19:25,750 --> 00:19:27,480
These pearls are so beautiful.

438
00:19:27,960 --> 00:19:29,110
Where is the mystery?

439
00:19:30,880 --> 00:19:31,880
These pearls

440
00:19:32,480 --> 00:19:34,750
hide stories.

441
00:19:45,480 --> 00:19:46,320
Girl,

442
00:19:46,590 --> 00:19:48,960
whether you want to or not,
you have to marry today.

443
00:19:50,360 --> 00:19:51,230
What's wrong?

444
00:19:51,240 --> 00:19:52,080
I saw it.

445
00:19:54,750 --> 00:19:55,590
Come.

446
00:19:58,480 --> 00:19:59,320
Stop!

447
00:19:59,790 --> 00:20:00,630
Lady.

448
00:20:01,300 --> 00:20:02,690
- Where are you running to?
- Help!

449
00:20:03,110 --> 00:20:03,950
- Help!
- Leave now.

450
00:20:21,550 --> 00:20:22,590
These are not pearls.

451
00:20:24,550 --> 00:20:25,390
They are tears.

452
00:20:26,030 --> 00:20:26,870
Tears?

453
00:20:28,680 --> 00:20:30,550
I saw it in an ancient book
of the Mu Family

454
00:20:31,400 --> 00:20:33,160
that a unique beast
known as the Fei Beast.

455
00:20:33,720 --> 00:20:36,030
Its blood could be used in medicine,
incense and charms.

456
00:20:36,200 --> 00:20:37,750
It made people joyful
and forget their worries.

457
00:20:38,550 --> 00:20:39,550
As its demon tier rises,

458
00:20:40,170 --> 00:20:41,790
it transforms into human form
and grows stronger.

459
00:20:42,680 --> 00:20:44,100
It could make those who were heartbroken

460
00:20:44,100 --> 00:20:45,400
shed tears and turn them into pearls.

461
00:20:47,270 --> 00:20:48,510
By discarding this pearl,

462
00:20:52,550 --> 00:20:54,550
one could discard
the sorrowful memories.

463
00:20:56,310 --> 00:20:58,030
So these pearls contain

464
00:20:58,680 --> 00:21:00,310
the memories of the women

465
00:21:00,640 --> 00:21:02,160
within Huazhe.

466
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:04,480
That seems to be true.

467
00:21:05,440 --> 00:21:06,280
Back then,

468
00:21:07,400 --> 00:21:09,510
after reading these tragic stories,

469
00:21:09,750 --> 00:21:11,070
I was deeply moved.

470
00:21:11,440 --> 00:21:12,280
I couldn't help

471
00:21:12,720 --> 00:21:15,110
but record them all one by one.

472
00:21:15,400 --> 00:21:17,720
Then I compiled them into
scripts with slight modifications

473
00:21:17,920 --> 00:21:18,920
and sold them.

474
00:21:19,480 --> 00:21:20,320
Unexpectedly,

475
00:21:21,000 --> 00:21:21,980
they became very popular.

476
00:21:23,000 --> 00:21:24,720
Isn't this still plagiarism?

477
00:21:24,720 --> 00:21:26,480
How can you use
others' tragic life stories

478
00:21:26,480 --> 00:21:27,480
to make money?

479
00:21:27,640 --> 00:21:29,590
Well, this is just borrowing ideas.

480
00:21:30,110 --> 00:21:31,030
Besides,

481
00:21:31,640 --> 00:21:33,030
who would have thought

482
00:21:33,030 --> 00:21:34,160
that the story contained here

483
00:21:34,160 --> 00:21:35,400
could actually be true?

484
00:21:36,750 --> 00:21:37,590
Moreover,

485
00:21:38,480 --> 00:21:39,400
I faced retribution.

486
00:21:42,880 --> 00:21:44,880
Just when my scripts were selling well,

487
00:21:46,200 --> 00:21:47,640
I never expected

488
00:21:49,070 --> 00:21:50,830
the owner of Huazhe,

489
00:21:51,830 --> 00:21:52,670
Liuniang,

490
00:21:53,640 --> 00:21:54,790
would come back to find me.

491
00:21:56,590 --> 00:21:57,960
It was then that I realized

492
00:22:00,160 --> 00:22:01,200
she was not human,

493
00:22:03,200 --> 00:22:04,160
but a demon.

494
00:22:08,550 --> 00:22:09,390
That day,

495
00:22:09,830 --> 00:22:12,240
when I was dreaming of making a fortune,

496
00:22:13,200 --> 00:22:14,480
she appeared.

497
00:22:49,570 --> 00:22:50,410
Oh my gosh.

498
00:23:07,110 --> 00:23:08,960
Was she here to seek revenge on you?

499
00:23:11,510 --> 00:23:12,350
No,

500
00:23:13,110 --> 00:23:14,160
quite the opposite.

501
00:23:15,030 --> 00:23:16,350
She came specifically to find me

502
00:23:17,070 --> 00:23:18,370
and gave me something.

503
00:23:19,830 --> 00:23:20,850
It was

504
00:23:21,880 --> 00:23:23,310
this half red pearl.

505
00:23:47,070 --> 00:23:48,550
I want to see them fly

506
00:23:48,750 --> 00:23:49,880
the largest Unity Lantern.

507
00:23:53,000 --> 00:23:53,920
Take care, come again.

508
00:23:54,790 --> 00:23:55,630
Girl,

509
00:23:55,640 --> 00:23:56,480
buy a lantern?

510
00:23:56,770 --> 00:23:57,660
See which one you like.

511
00:23:59,480 --> 00:24:00,480
(Where is my bracelet?)

512
00:24:05,400 --> 00:24:06,680
Lady, are you looking for this?

513
00:24:09,860 --> 00:24:12,740
(Zhao Qinghuan)

514
00:24:14,300 --> 00:24:16,340
(Mu Rong'er)

515
00:24:39,820 --> 00:24:46,140
(Mu Rong'er)

516
00:24:46,880 --> 00:24:48,880
What name should we give him?

517
00:24:49,000 --> 00:24:50,680
(I miss you in autumn under the galaxy.)
This child

518
00:24:50,680 --> 00:24:52,940
(I dressed up to tell the pear blossom.)
is what both of us expected,

519
00:24:53,030 --> 00:24:54,240
what about calling him Ziqi?

520
00:24:55,100 --> 00:24:56,300
(Wind rises, the beauty might leave.)

521
00:24:56,310 --> 00:24:57,440
Ziqi.

522
00:24:57,440 --> 00:24:58,900
(The insects frequently laugh
at my doubts.)

523
00:24:59,680 --> 00:25:00,520
Zhao,

524
00:25:00,640 --> 00:25:01,560
who exactly are you?

525
00:25:01,750 --> 00:25:03,890
The imperial family has already sent
a Demon Catcher

526
00:25:04,110 --> 00:25:05,000
to come and find you.

527
00:25:06,510 --> 00:25:07,720
If they dare to act recklessly,

528
00:25:07,880 --> 00:25:08,720
I will kill you.

529
00:25:13,310 --> 00:25:14,270
If one day,

530
00:25:14,750 --> 00:25:15,830
the world changes,

531
00:25:16,480 --> 00:25:17,830
humans and demons can coexist

532
00:25:18,310 --> 00:25:19,830
and live under the daylight.

533
00:25:21,030 --> 00:25:22,110
Our family of three

534
00:25:23,110 --> 00:25:24,240
will surely reunite again.

535
00:25:32,750 --> 00:25:33,590
And then?

536
00:25:33,790 --> 00:25:34,640
Why did it stop?

537
00:25:35,880 --> 00:25:38,350
The memories in this half pearl
are just that much.

538
00:25:39,160 --> 00:25:40,000
Later,

539
00:25:40,680 --> 00:25:41,760
Liuniang came to me and said

540
00:25:42,020 --> 00:25:42,880
she could overlook

541
00:25:42,880 --> 00:25:45,480
the fact that I exchanged the memories
in those pearls for money.

542
00:25:45,680 --> 00:25:46,960
But there is one condition.

543
00:25:47,310 --> 00:25:49,290
She asked me
to continue writing these stories,

544
00:25:50,030 --> 00:25:52,350
especially about the love story

545
00:25:52,350 --> 00:25:54,030
in this half red pearl,

546
00:25:54,270 --> 00:25:56,720
spreading it widely so that
as many people as possible

547
00:25:56,720 --> 00:25:58,200
know about it.

548
00:25:58,350 --> 00:25:59,310
She said that this way

549
00:25:59,790 --> 00:26:02,350
there was a possibility
for the child inside,

550
00:26:02,830 --> 00:26:03,880
Ziqi,

551
00:26:04,480 --> 00:26:05,510
to come back and find her.

552
00:26:06,270 --> 00:26:07,750
She specifically told me,

553
00:26:08,030 --> 00:26:10,400
if one day you really come,

554
00:26:10,720 --> 00:26:12,160
I must tell you

555
00:26:13,680 --> 00:26:14,590
to find her.

556
00:26:18,920 --> 00:26:21,790
So the one who wants Ziqi to appear

557
00:26:22,270 --> 00:26:23,550
is this Liuniang.

558
00:26:23,920 --> 00:26:24,760
That's right.

559
00:26:25,400 --> 00:26:27,200
She now comes every year

560
00:26:27,480 --> 00:26:28,350
to ask me

561
00:26:28,350 --> 00:26:30,160
when I can find the child in this story.

562
00:26:30,550 --> 00:26:32,200
She said if I can't find him this year,

563
00:26:33,000 --> 00:26:34,160
she will strangle me.

564
00:26:35,240 --> 00:26:36,200
Ziqi, Zi…

565
00:26:36,790 --> 00:26:37,640
Girl, wait a moment.

566
00:26:39,200 --> 00:26:40,040
Take this.

567
00:26:40,400 --> 00:26:41,590
This was left by Liuniang.

568
00:26:41,920 --> 00:26:42,960
Inside is a map.

569
00:26:43,400 --> 00:26:44,400
She lives

570
00:26:44,500 --> 00:26:45,830
in the mountains outside the town,

