574
00:26:51,960 --> 00:26:52,800
Girl,

575
00:26:55,240 --> 00:26:57,400
you're helping him find his memories.

576
00:26:58,790 --> 00:26:59,630
Have you forgotten

577
00:27:01,200 --> 00:27:02,920
something yourself?

578
00:27:08,400 --> 00:27:09,240
Girl,

579
00:27:09,830 --> 00:27:10,670
you must remember,

580
00:27:12,350 --> 00:27:13,790
life is but a fleeting dream.

581
00:27:14,830 --> 00:27:16,000
You and him,

582
00:27:17,590 --> 00:27:19,880
only one can wake up.

583
00:27:30,750 --> 00:27:33,310
This is a map
that Lord Jiyue just gave me.

584
00:27:35,790 --> 00:27:38,270
Following this path
to climb two mountains,

585
00:27:38,600 --> 00:27:40,720
we will reach the Wuyou Water Fort,
where Liuniang is.

586
00:27:48,680 --> 00:27:49,520
Ziqi,

587
00:27:50,240 --> 00:27:51,920
are you starting to remember something?

588
00:27:54,400 --> 00:27:55,240
I finally understand

589
00:27:56,790 --> 00:27:58,440
why I have no memory of anything

590
00:27:59,430 --> 00:28:00,550
before I was seven years old.

591
00:28:03,030 --> 00:28:05,790
It's her who tampered with my memory.

592
00:28:06,000 --> 00:28:07,310
She cast a Worry-Free Curse on me.

593
00:28:08,720 --> 00:28:10,680
Then I began to wander aimlessly

594
00:28:11,720 --> 00:28:13,310
until I stumbled into the Mu Mansion

595
00:28:14,110 --> 00:28:15,110
and met my sister.

596
00:28:17,350 --> 00:28:18,400
I could never figure out

597
00:28:19,030 --> 00:28:21,000
who exactly wanted to
tamper with my memory.

598
00:28:25,160 --> 00:28:26,000
I never expected

599
00:28:27,720 --> 00:28:28,960
