609
00:28:56,590 --> 00:28:57,430
Ziqi,

610
00:28:57,980 --> 00:28:59,100
don't push yourself too hard.

611
00:28:59,750 --> 00:29:01,070
I know you're very sad.

612
00:29:12,170 --> 00:29:13,480
