613
00:29:16,550 --> 00:29:17,390
Yes.

614
00:29:18,500 --> 00:29:20,400
The Qingyi Marquis abandoned
his wife and child.

615
00:29:21,880 --> 00:29:22,720
But…

616
00:29:24,790 --> 00:29:25,630
But…

617
00:29:27,440 --> 00:29:28,280
But

618
00:29:28,880 --> 00:29:30,680
it's not your fault.

619
00:29:32,200 --> 00:29:33,130
But she didn't think so.

620
00:29:35,880 --> 00:29:36,720
She's like

621
00:29:38,160 --> 00:29:39,720
shedding a burden.

622
00:29:41,160 --> 00:29:42,440
She left in a great hurry.

623
00:29:44,270 --> 00:29:45,880
She didn't even glance back at me.

624
00:30:02,400 --> 00:30:03,400
Actually, in the past,

625
00:30:03,400 --> 00:30:04,240
she was just a

626
00:30:04,920 --> 00:30:06,110
vague shadow.

627
00:30:07,480 --> 00:30:09,000
She had no impact on me.

628
00:30:11,440 --> 00:30:12,350
But in recent days,

629
00:30:13,960 --> 00:30:15,240
my memory has gradually returned.

630
00:30:17,350 --> 00:30:19,030
Many questions
I hadn't considered before

631
00:30:19,480 --> 00:30:21,160
kept appearing in my mind.

632
00:30:24,160 --> 00:30:25,000
Miaomiao,

633
00:30:26,790 --> 00:30:27,630
do you think

634
00:30:30,350 --> 00:30:31,240
she is still alive?

635
00:30:33,200 --> 00:30:34,210
Has she ever regretted it?

636
00:30:36,110 --> 00:30:36,950
Did she

637
00:30:40,200 --> 00:30:41,040
ever love me?

638
00:30:50,210 --> 00:30:51,220
All these years,

639
00:30:52,790 --> 00:30:54,350
Liuniang has been looking for you.

640
00:30:55,510 --> 00:30:56,350
I think

641
00:30:57,310 --> 00:30:58,480
could it be your mother

642
00:30:59,070 --> 00:31:00,400
entrusted her to find you.

643
00:31:01,310 --> 00:31:02,590
She also wants to see you.

644
00:31:06,680 --> 00:31:07,520
Ziqi,

645
00:31:09,350 --> 00:31:10,640
do you want to see her?

646
00:31:16,270 --> 00:31:17,110
I don't know.

647
00:31:19,900 --> 00:31:20,840
But as things stand now,

648
00:31:22,310 --> 00:31:23,550
I must go to see her.

649
00:31:40,700 --> 00:31:42,540
(Cainan County)

650
00:31:42,550 --> 00:31:43,480
Someone is over there.

651
00:31:43,720 --> 00:31:44,560
Let's go and inquire.

652
00:31:45,900 --> 00:31:47,060
Fellow villagers, please stop.

653
00:31:47,600 --> 00:31:49,530
We are here to find
the Mysterious Cold Silkworm.

654
00:31:50,270 --> 00:31:52,400
