657
00:31:58,440 --> 00:32:00,510
You'd better look for it elsewhere.

658
00:32:09,310 --> 00:32:10,150
Mr. Dong.

659
00:32:22,980 --> 00:32:24,700
(Liuru Village, Cainan County)

660
00:32:24,720 --> 00:32:25,880
You're out for a stroll?

661
00:32:27,050 --> 00:32:28,360
Yes.

662
00:32:32,450 --> 00:32:33,500
Come, I'll give you a hand.

663
00:32:33,500 --> 00:32:34,400
