669
00:32:42,860 --> 00:32:44,480
So I air out the blankets.

670
00:32:45,610 --> 00:32:46,450
Okay.

671
00:32:52,160 --> 00:32:53,400
Look, it's here.

672
00:32:55,160 --> 00:32:56,590
