673
00:32:57,110 --> 00:32:58,270
See who's back!

674
00:32:58,830 --> 00:32:59,670
Who is it?

675
00:32:59,880 --> 00:33:00,900
Everyone, come and see!

676
00:33:01,000 --> 00:33:02,000
See who's back!

677
00:33:03,310 --> 00:33:04,150
My husband,

678
00:33:04,150 --> 00:33:05,350
why are you making such a fuss?

679
00:33:06,070 --> 00:33:07,480
Come and see!

680
00:33:12,270 --> 00:33:13,200
Come over!

681
00:33:13,780 --> 00:33:14,620
My wife,

682
00:33:14,620 --> 00:33:16,990
- Let's go, take a look.
- look, do you still recognize him?

683
00:33:17,680 --> 00:33:18,520
Who is it?

684
00:33:18,590 --> 00:33:19,430
Mrs. Zhang.

685
00:33:21,030 --> 00:33:21,870
Hurry.

686
00:33:22,310 --> 00:33:23,470
Come and see who this is.

687
00:33:24,070 --> 00:33:24,910
Come over quickly.

688
00:33:25,550 --> 00:33:26,790
Come on, hurry.

689
00:33:27,300 --> 00:33:28,320
Everyone, come and look.

690
00:33:30,270 --> 00:33:32,270
- Isn't this…?
- Who is this?

691
00:33:35,400 --> 00:33:36,480
I don't remember.

692
00:33:40,680 --> 00:33:41,520
Mrs. Zhang,

693
00:33:42,150 --> 00:33:43,200
can't recognize him, right?

694
00:33:44,200 --> 00:33:45,110
When he was a child,

695
00:33:45,400 --> 00:33:47,290
he loved the yellow rice cake
you made the most.

696
00:33:50,200 --> 00:33:51,040
Maodan?

697
00:33:52,830 --> 00:33:53,830
It's really Maodan!

698
00:33:54,590 --> 00:33:55,750
Maodan is back!

699
00:33:56,920 --> 00:33:58,310
- Maodan!
- Maodan is back!

700
00:33:58,550 --> 00:33:59,590
Maodan is back!

701
00:34:00,110 --> 00:34:00,950
Maodan!

702
00:34:01,000 --> 00:34:02,000
Come, let me see.

703
00:34:02,960 --> 00:34:03,800
Mrs. Zhang.

704
00:34:05,640 --> 00:34:06,480
Mrs. Niu.

705
00:34:07,500 --> 00:34:09,470
- You are back.
- Come and see!

706
00:34:10,110 --> 00:34:11,920
He brings back such a beautiful wife.

707
00:34:29,400 --> 00:34:30,240
Mrs. Zhang,

708
00:34:34,400 --> 00:34:35,240
Mrs. Niu,

709
00:34:37,030 --> 00:34:37,870
you…

710
00:34:39,880 --> 00:34:40,840
you all are still alive.

711
00:34:47,630 --> 00:34:49,710
You haven't come back for ten years.

712
00:34:49,900 --> 00:34:51,880
You probably don't know
the savior of our village.

713
00:34:52,110 --> 00:34:53,590
It's the Lady Divine Doctor.

714
00:34:55,760 --> 00:34:57,030
Lady Divine Doctor?

715
00:34:57,670 --> 00:34:58,510
Yes.

716
00:34:58,520 --> 00:34:59,760
She's also known as Shiniang.

717
00:35:00,150 --> 00:35:00,990
It was she

718
00:35:01,280 --> 00:35:03,400
who saved the lives of
everyone in our village.

719
00:35:03,960 --> 00:35:04,800
Ten years ago,

720
00:35:05,000 --> 00:35:07,030
she and her husband
passed through our village.

721
00:35:07,630 --> 00:35:09,860
Our villagers were injured by a demon

722
00:35:10,320 --> 00:35:11,390
and fell to the ground.

723
00:35:12,110 --> 00:35:14,360
Shiniang, with her kind heart

724
00:35:14,370 --> 00:35:15,490
and excellent medical skills,

725
00:35:15,920 --> 00:35:18,000
saved the lives of everyone
in our village.

726
00:35:18,590 --> 00:35:20,030
Thank heavens.

727
00:35:20,510 --> 00:35:21,760
If it weren't for her,

728
00:35:21,920 --> 00:35:24,070
everyone in our village would have died.

729
00:35:24,920 --> 00:35:27,030
She lives
at the west end of the village.

730
00:35:27,840 --> 00:35:29,710
Just follow this road to the end,

731
00:35:30,070 --> 00:35:31,690
there's a yard with a fence.

732
00:35:32,000 --> 00:35:32,960
That's her home.

733
00:35:42,760 --> 00:35:43,760
This should be the place.

734
00:35:45,700 --> 00:35:46,400
What Divine Doctor

735
00:35:46,400 --> 00:35:47,450
can bring the dead back to life?

736
00:35:57,760 --> 00:35:58,600
Hello,

737
00:35:58,700 --> 00:35:59,710
is the Divine Doctor here?

738
00:36:01,300 --> 00:36:02,390
Who is looking for Shiniang?

739
00:36:06,960 --> 00:36:07,800
I am Li Zhun,

740
00:36:07,860 --> 00:36:09,180
(Li Zhun, Merchant)
Shiniang's husband.

741
00:36:09,190 --> 00:36:10,590
Are you two here for treatment?

742
00:36:11,550 --> 00:36:12,630
Where does your demonic aura

743
00:36:12,840 --> 00:36:13,680
come from?

744
00:36:13,920 --> 00:36:14,760
What?

745
00:36:16,510 --> 00:36:17,350
Fuyi!

746
00:36:21,510 --> 00:36:22,320
Stop!

747
00:36:22,320 --> 00:36:24,790
(Divine Doctor Shiniang)
Who is bullying people at my doorstep?

748
00:36:32,500 --> 00:36:33,660
So you two are Demon Catchers.

749
00:36:34,200 --> 00:36:35,220
I apologize for the disrespect.

750
00:36:37,510 --> 00:36:38,760
We were too abrupt.

751
00:36:39,440 --> 00:36:40,900
We didn't make it clear

752
00:36:41,030 --> 00:36:42,030
before we acted rashly.

753
00:36:42,400 --> 00:36:43,360
I didn't expect

754
00:36:44,030 --> 00:36:45,400
the Mysterious Cold Silkworm

755
00:36:45,550 --> 00:36:47,360
to be the medicinal guide
for treating asthma.

756
00:36:48,590 --> 00:36:49,430
That's right.

757
00:36:50,510 --> 00:36:51,890
Thanks to this thing.

758
00:36:52,850 --> 00:36:53,970
Its silk is used in medicine,

759
00:36:54,840 --> 00:36:57,110
so that the condition of
both Chuchu and I has stabilized.

760
00:36:59,440 --> 00:37:00,280
Chuchu,

761
00:37:00,290 --> 00:37:02,450
(Chuchu, Li Zhun's daughter)
come and greet the guests.

762
00:37:09,400 --> 00:37:10,920
My daughter Chuchu is spoiled.

763
00:37:11,530 --> 00:37:13,230
Does your daughter
also suffer from asthma?

764
00:37:14,320 --> 00:37:15,270
Yes. It is a misfortune.

765
00:37:16,230 --> 00:37:17,520
Fortunately,

766
00:37:18,670 --> 00:37:19,840
I met Shiniang.

767
00:38:24,070 --> 00:38:24,910
However, later on,

768
00:38:26,150 --> 00:38:27,230
Chuchu's condition worsened.

769
00:38:28,000 --> 00:38:29,070
Shiniang and I took her

770
00:38:29,590 --> 00:38:30,670
to seek medicine everywhere.

771
00:38:31,320 --> 00:38:32,160
Shiniang said,

772
00:38:32,670 --> 00:38:33,750
if we could find

773
00:38:33,800 --> 00:38:35,650
a demon spirit called
Mysterious Cold Silkworm,

774
00:38:36,000 --> 00:38:37,470
using the silk it produces as medicine

775
00:38:38,030 --> 00:38:39,140
with her medical skills,

776
00:38:39,940 --> 00:38:42,290
there would be no life in this world
that couldn't be saved.

777
00:38:43,670 --> 00:38:44,510
However,

778
00:38:45,860 --> 00:38:47,230
the silkworm is truly hard to find.

779
00:38:49,000 --> 00:38:50,750
I travelled through
the deep mountains with Shiniang,

780
00:38:52,030 --> 00:38:53,400
but in the end I couldn't hold on

