807
00:40:26,710 --> 00:40:27,550
Hold on tight.

808
00:40:27,550 --> 00:40:29,510
Hello, is Liuniang here?

809
00:40:29,630 --> 00:40:31,620
We came here with the map

810
00:40:31,710 --> 00:40:32,630
