821
00:40:57,110 --> 00:40:59,000
We are all women, all sisters.

822
00:40:59,710 --> 00:41:00,960
No one will be hurt.

823
00:41:02,480 --> 00:41:04,360
Is Liuniang the one in charge here?

824
00:41:04,880 --> 00:41:06,440
Yes, Liuniang is a very good

825
00:41:06,550 --> 00:41:07,710
and very kind female demon.

826
00:41:08,150 --> 00:41:09,550
She built this fort by herself

827
00:41:09,710 --> 00:41:10,550
to take us in.

828
00:41:10,960 --> 00:41:11,800
She said

829
00:41:11,880 --> 00:41:14,150
women who were not accepted by the world

830
00:41:14,440 --> 00:41:15,800
